cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the phenomenon of evasion attacks using adversarial examples for deep learning systems, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and defenses against adversarial attacks (cs.AI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.CR, followed by cs.AI and cs.NE.
